Detailed occupational earnings are available for metropolitan and non-metropolitan areas, broad geographic regions, and on a national basis. The index component of the NCS (ECI) measures changes in labor costs. Average hourly employer cost for employee compensation is presented in the ECEC.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>compensation-statistics</dcat:keyword>     <foaf:homepage
